DISNEY CHANNEL.

DISNEY CHANNEL IS A CABLE/SATELLITE NETWORK SERVICE THAT TARGETS CHILDREN AND FAMILIES.

SHOWS DEVELOPED AND PRODUCED INTERNALLY FOR INITIAL EXHIBITION ON DISNEY CHANNEL INCLUDE LIVE-ACTION COMEDY SERIES, ANIMATED PROGRAMMING AND EDUCATIONAL PRESCHOOL SERIES, AS WELL AS PROJECTS FOR THE DISNEY CHANNEL ORIGINAL MOVIE FRANCHISE, INCLUDING

THIS YEARS

JUMP IN

AND

