AND

THE REPLACEMENTS.

DISNEY CHANNEL ALSO OPERATES IN MORE

THAN 20 MARKETS OUTSIDE THE UNITED STATES. INTERNATIONAL PROGRAMMING CONSISTS PRIMARILY OF THE COMPANYS ORIGINALLY PRODUCED SERIES AND MOVIES, PRODUCTS ACQUIRED FROM THIRD PARTIES AND LOCALLY-PRODUCED PROGRAMMING. WE CONTINUE TO EXPLORE THE

FURTHER DEVELOPMENT OF DISNEY CHANNEL IN OTHER COUNTRIES AROUND THE WORLD.

