PRINCIPAL AREAS: GOLDEN STATE, HOLLYWOOD PICTURES BACKLOT, PARADISE PIER AND A BUGS LAND. THESE AREAS INCLUDE RIDES, ATTRACTIONS, SHOWS, RESTAURANTS, MERCHANDISE SHOPS AND REFRESHMENT STANDS.

