LIQUIDATED AND THE SALES OF A CABLE TELEVISION EQUITY INVESTMENT AND A MAGAZINE BUSINESS GENERATED $81 MILLION.

DURING FISCAL 2005, THE

COMPANY RECEIVED $100 MILLION FOR WORKING CAPITAL TRANSFERRED TO THE BUYER OF THE DISNEY STORE NORTH AMERICA AND $29 MILLION FROM THE SALE OF THE MIGHTY DUCKS OF ANAHEIM.

