THE FOLLOWING DISPOSALS OCCURRED DURING FISCAL 2006 AND FISCAL 2005.



A CABLE TELEVISION EQUITY INVESTMENT IN SPAIN WAS SOLD FOR $67 MILLION ON NOVEMBER 23, 2005, RESULTING IN A PRE-TAX GAIN OF $57 MILLION.

