PARIS (EXCEPT FOR WALT DISNEY STUDIOS PARK) WITH A NET BOOK VALUE OF APPROXIMATELY 1.5 BILLION ($2.1 BILLION AT SEPTEMBER 29, 2007 EXCHANGE RATES). AT SEPTEMBER 29, 2007, THE TOTAL BALANCE OUTSTANDING WAS 401 MILLION ($568

