AND INCLUDES AMORTIZATION OF PREVIOUSLY CAPITALIZED EQUITY-BASED COMPENSATION COSTS. CAPITALIZED EQUITY-BASED COMPENSATION TOTALED $103 MILLION, $52 MILLION AND $18 MILLION IN 2007, 2006 AND 2005, RESPECTIVELY.

