BINOMIAL VALUATION MODEL WAS NOT REASONABLY AVAILABLE. THE METHODOLOGY UTILIZED TO DETERMINE THE ASSUMPTIONS IN THE BLACK-SCHOLES MODEL WAS CONSISTENT WITH THAT USED BY THE COMPANY FOR ITS OPTION-PRICING MODELS.

